songs.title: We All Fall Down*
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I pledge with the morning light
I gotta [?] just to fall behind
Breathe and die
I say, I don't want to go back
I don't want to go back
Take me home, tonight
Breathe and die

[Chorus]
[?]
We fall down, we all fall down
[?]
We fall down, we all fall down

[Verse 2]
I take these [?]
[?]
Breathe and die

[Chorus]
[?]
To walk out, to walk out
[?]
We fall down, we all fall down

[Bridge]
I try to speak my mind to you
But I tell you what to do
Don't let it feel so broken
Oh, I [?]
And the seasons [?]
You know, you know I'll be with you
I'll be with you, ooh, oh!

[Chorus]
[?]
We fall down, we all fall down
[?]
We fall down, we all fall down
